com.tsgrp.migration.node.attribute

Class NodeAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.node.attribute.NodeAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>

    public class NodeAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>
    This class represents a node's attribute, which has a name and AttributeDataType and a list of values.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      protected AttributeDataType dataType
      The data type of the attribute, set in constructor and immutable thereafter.
      protected java.lang.String name
      The name of the attribute (used as the key in the MigrationNode's attributes Map), set in constructor and immutable thereafter.
      protected java.util.List<java.lang.Object> values
      This attribute's values (for a repeating attribute), or single value as the only item in the list, as Java primitive wrapper datatype objects (Integer, String, etc.).
